00-pct-applications-behind-the-breakthroughs-86102"},{"date":"2026-06-12","title":"Develop the Chinese PCT Applicants' Guide","content":"A Chinese-language PCT applicants' guide resource supporting access to practical PCT information.","source":"WIPO PCT Legal","category":"PCT Guide","link":"https://pctlegal.wipo.int/eGuide/view-doc.xhtml?doc-code=pctip&doc-type=guide&doc-lang=zh"},{"date":"2026-05-28","title":"PCT user stories including Google, Apple and TIME Best Inventions, and more","content":"A short reflection on turning complex international patent information into practical, accessible guidance for innovators.","source":"Na Li on LinkedIn","category":"PCT Story","link":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/na-li-wkc/"},{"date":"2026-04-24","title":"Celebrating World Intellectual Property Day 2024 and 2025","content":"Highlights from a campaign connecting creativity, innovation, and the people who bring new ideas to life.","source":"WIPO Website","category":"Campaign","link":"https://www.wipo.int/en/web/ipday"},{"date":"2026-03-12","title":"Digital transformation resource spotlight","content":"A hub provides a wide range of quality publications on a range of digital transformation topics, including smart sustainable cities, cities’ actions to tackle COVID-19, digital public infrastructure, artificial intelligence, Internet of things, blockchain, digital twin, metaverse and virtual worlds and digital transformation trends.","source":"Na Li on ITU Website","category":"Digital Transformation","link":"https://www.itu.int/cities/dt-resource-hub/"}]}]},{"type":"card","id":"projects","config":{"type":"card","title":"Projects and Achievements","description":"Selected involved projects and achievements, including social media platform, newsletters, digital campaigns and projects.","layout":"grid","items":[{"title":"PCT Stories","subtitle":"Original LinkedIn series","date":"Ongoing","content":"A growing collection of practical stories explaining how the Patent Cooperation Treaty supports innovators across borders.","tags":["PCT","Patent","Storytelling"],"link":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/na-li-wkc/","image":"/projects/pct-stories.png","photoCredit":"Credits: Lina"},{"title":"PCT Newsletters","subtitle":"Knowledge and updates","content":"Curated developments, practical guidance, and stories from the international patent system from September 2025 to January 2026; Drafted a proposal for the PCT Newsletter revamp.","tags":["Newsletter","Patents"],"link":"https://www.wipo.int/en/web/pct-system/newslett/index","image":"/projects/pct-newsletter.png","photoCredit":"Credits: WIPO"},{"title":"WIPO Knowledge and Resources","subtitle":"Social media content","content":"Professional posts connecting audiences with useful intellectual property tools and learning materials, from launch in 2024 to January 2025.","tags":["Knowledge","LinkedIn"],"link":"https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/wipo-knowledge-and-resources","image":"/projects/wipo-knowledge.png","photoCredit":"Credits: WIPO"},{"title":"WKC Newsletter","subtitle":"Knowledge communication","content":"A newsletter concept presenting timely resources, expert perspectives, and practical learning opportunities. Monthly updates from 2024 to January 2025.","tags":["Editorial","Knowledge"],"link":"https://www.wipo.int/en/web/newsletters/archives?newsletter=wkc","image":"/projects/wkc-newsletter.png","photoCredit":"Credits: WIPO"},{"title":"World IP Day","subtitle":"Global digital campaigns","content":"Campaigns in celebrating World IP Day on 26 April each year. Involved in co-managing of the IP Day 2024 themed on IP and SDGs and 2025 themed IP and music, including compiled website content, coordinate visuals, co-managed the Youth Video Competition, assisted in developing tool such as [IP and SDG tool - connecting the dots between IP and the SDGs](https://multimedia.wipo.int/exhibitions/ip-sdgs/index.htm), assisted in internal coordination and member states meetings, managed the [changemakers' gallery](https://www.wipo.int/en/web/ipday/wipd-2024-gallery), [World IP Day events calendar](https://www.wipo.int/en/web/ipday/events-calendar), assisting in setting up events at WIPO premises.","tags":["Campaign","World IP Day"],"link":"https://www.wipo.int/web/ipday","image":"/projects/world-ip-day.png","photoCredit":"Credits: WIPO"},{"title":"Youth Video Competition","subtitle":"Youth engagement","content":"An international storytelling initiative inviting young creators to share ideas through short-form video.","tags":["Youth","Video"],"link":"https://www.wipo.int/en/web/ipday/2025/video-competition","image":"/projects/youth-video.png","photoCredit":"Credits: WIPO"},{"title":"Digital Transformation Resource Hub","subtitle":"Open-access free publications","content":"A structured collection of quality publications on digital transformation topics, including smart sustainable cities, cities’ actions to tackle COVID-19, digital public infrastructure, artificial intelligence, Internet of things, blockchain, digital twin, metaverse and virtual worlds and digital transformation trends.","tags":["Digital","Resource Hub"],"link":"https://www.itu.int/cities/dt-resource-hub/","image":"/projects/digital-hub.png","photoCredit":"Credits: ITU/Lina"},{"title":"Data visualization showcase","subtitle":"User interface and data design","content":"Good at data visualization and user interface design.\n\n[PCT Contracting States (non-use)](https://public.flourish.studio/story/3132921/)\n\n[Patent filing Infographic](https://public.flourish.studio/visualisation/20746595/)","tags":["Data visualization","UI design"],"image":"https://public.flourish.studio/visualisation/20746595/thumbnail","photoCredit":"Credits: Lina"}]}},{"type":"card","id":"gallery","config":{"type":"card","title":"Photo Gallery","description":"Selected professional moments, field visits, conferences, and knowledge-sharing activities.","layout":"gallery","items":[{"title":"Apple's latest PCT filing 2025","subtitle":"Occassionaly post patent stories on Na's LinkedIn, topics on big technology companies, interesting inventions and neglected inventions in our daily life, and more","image":"/gallery/photos/apple-pct-2025.jpg","images":["/gallery/photos/apple-pct-2025.jpg","/gallery/photos/best-inventions-2025.jpg"],"photoCredit":"Photo: Lina"},{"title":"Community visit in Kenya","subtitle":"Field engagement and local connection in the hospital","image":"/gallery/photos/community-visit.jpg","photoCredit":"Photo: Gelise"},{"title":"Youth creativity workshop","subtitle":"Creative learning and exchange with art, enjoy drawings together and sprint out new connections","image":"/gallery/photos/youth-creativity-workshop.jpg","photoCredit":"Photo: Gelise"},{"title":"Innovation Exhibition of Inventions Geneva at Palexpo","subtitle":"Showcasing the WIPO Virtual World of Innovation and Creativity using VR headsets","image":"/gallery/photos/innovation-exhibition.jpg","photoCredit":"Photo: Danilo"},{"title":"World IP Day and the SDGs","subtitle":"Building a common future with innovation and creativity","image":"/gallery/photos/world-ip-day-sdgs.jpg","photoCredit":"Photo: Lise","embed":{"src":"https://www.linkedin.com/embed/feed/update/urn:li:ugcPost:7189643134207725568?compact=1","title":"Embedded post","height":399}},{"title":"Leading tours for visitors to Yakuanoi World","subtitle":"On traditional knowledge and genetic resources","image":"/gallery/photos/wipo-event-portrait.jpg","photoCredit":"Photo: Lina"},{"title":"PCT team gathering for Lina's farewell","subtitle":"Group sharing and warm moments in my life, collect life wisdoms to carry on for the rest of my life.","image":"/gallery/photos/professional-photo-na-li.jpg","images":["/gallery/photos/professional-photo-na-li.jpg","/gallery/photos/pct-team-farewell-selfie.jpg"],"photoCredit":"Photo: ZLY"},{"title":"Genetic resources conference","subtitle":"Lina's volunteering work at the Diplomatic Conference on Genetic Resources and Traditional Knowledge, at reception table in disseminating souvenirs.","image":"/gallery/photos/genetic-resources-conference.jpg","photoCredit":"Photo: WIPO/Berrod"},{"title":"YEPs in 2024","subtitle":"WIPO's Young Expert onboard meeting with Director General","image":"/gallery/photos/yeps-2024-group.jpg","images":["/gallery/photos/yeps-2024-group.jpg","/gallery/photos/yeps-meeting-2024.jpg","/gallery/photos/yep26.jpeg"],"photoCredit":"Photo: WIPO/Berrod"}]}}]}},"defaultLocale":"en"}],["$","$Lb",null,{"children":"$Lc"}],null,["$","$Ld",null,{"children":["$Le","$Lf",["$","$L10",null,{"promise":"$@11"}]]}]]}],{},null,false]},null,false],["$","$1","h",{"children":[null,["$","$1","TcwGErHLXi-4CSLqly9KF",{"children":[["$","$L12",null,{"children":"$L13"}],null]}],null]}],false]],"m":"$undefined","G":["$14","$undefined"],"s":false,"S":true}
